141 (2) A rule that is less stringent or extensive in
142 scope, coverage, or effect than any federal law or regulation
143 setting a standard regarding the same or a substantially
144 similar topic or that is substantively equivalent to a federal
145 law or regulation.
146 (3) A rule that would repeal or modify an existing rule
147 to be less stringent or extensive in scope, coverage, or
148 effect.
149 (4) An emergency rule adopted pursuant to Section
150 41-22-5, Code of Alabama 1975.
151 Section 2. This act shall become effective on October
152 1, 2026.
